{"id":290713,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-江苏冯兰美等人举报黑监狱，南通检察院/","date":"2013-04-26T16:30:56Z","modified":"2013-04-26T16:30:56Z","title":"维权网 | 江苏冯兰美等人举报黑监狱，南通检察院避而不见（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>，江苏省南通如皋冯兰美与南通维权人士张亮、徐和平等一起到南通市检察院报案，举报如皋市公安局崔叶和以及如城镇政府官员打着举办法制教育学习班的名义对冯兰美非法拘禁，并对其实施虐待和侮辱。南通市检察院接待员竟然说，关于如皋市国务院举办法制教育学习班限制人身自由的案件，不属于检察院管辖。经张亮等据理力争，该接待员要向领导汇报，离开接待室。此后，接待室空无一人，久等不归。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>一早，即冯兰美逃出如皋黑监狱的次日，她与张亮、倪文华等一起到南通市公安局报案。该公安局称，国家工作人员非法拘禁公民，不属于公安机关管辖，而属于检察院管辖，建议去检察院报案。倪文华说，公安机关有义务将冯兰美的举报信转交检察院。但南通市公安局置之不理。冯兰美等当日下午赶到南通市检察院报案。但该检察院要冯兰美填写报案内容后，并无下文。这次是第二次报案了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p><span>冯兰美因去年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月遭遇如城镇政府偷拆，而向如皋法院起诉。该院百般刁难，直至去年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日，才准予立案，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>，如城镇政府将冯兰美关进黑监狱。期间，如皋政府马跃法官逼冯兰美撤诉；政府逼冯兰美签订拆迁补偿协议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>，如皋当局才释放冯兰美，非法拘禁达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">47</span><span>天。冯兰美不服，到北京上访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，如皋公安局崔叶和将冯兰美截访，并交如城镇政府，再次将冯兰美关进黑监狱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，冯兰美逃离如皋黑监狱。在关押期间，政府工作人员百般虐待冯兰美。冯兰美的女儿请求迎春派出所警察营救其母，却被恶警推倒。当时，冯兰美的女儿正怀孕，现在还在医院进行保胎治疗。</span><br /><span><br /></span></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wKNt5CR3Dow/UXqaml_RSVI/AAAAAAAAg9g/RZ52CePUvk0/s1600/2%E3%80%81%E5%86%AF%E5%85%B0%E7%BE%8E%E5%88%B0%E5%8D%97%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%9F%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%BE%E6%8A%A5%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wKNt5CR3Dow/UXqaml_RSVI/AAAAAAAAg9g/RZ52CePUvk0/s320/2%E3%80%81%E5%86%AF%E5%85%B0%E7%BE%8E%E5%88%B0%E5%8D%97%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%9F%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%BE%E6%8A%A5%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>冯兰美到南通市检察院举报黑监狱</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-RgUlKkCwswI/UXqan8lVzMI/AAAAAAAAg9s/3WDPvPzULBc/s1600/3%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%9F%E9%99%A2%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%85%E5%91%98%E6%BA%9C%E8%B5%B0%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%85%E5%AE%A4%E7%A9%BA%E6%97%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-RgUlKkCwswI/UXqan8lVzMI/AAAAAAAAg9s/3WDPvPzULBc/s320/3%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%9F%E9%99%A2%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%85%E5%91%98%E6%BA%9C%E8%B5%B0%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%85%E5%AE%A4%E7%A9%BA%E6%97%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>南通市检察院接待员溜走后，接待室空无一人</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-V7jiv-AWp3U/UXqamOY2S3I/AAAAAAAAg9c/-20-dqHwfSE/s1600/1%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%9F%E9%99%A2%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%85%E5%91%98.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"301\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-V7jiv-AWp3U/UXqamOY2S3I/AAAAAAAAg9c/-20-dqHwfSE/s320/1%E3%80%81%E5%8D%97%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%9F%E9%99%A2%E6%8E%A5%E5%BE%85%E5%91%98.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>南通市检察院接待员</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>